          <history-note id="DLM374496"><amended-provision>Section 10(2)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>28 June 2006</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM373572">section 29(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Dog Control Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 23).</history-note>
