          <history-note id="DLM374801"><amended-provision>Section 10(8A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2003</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM229336">section 5(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Dog Control Amendment Act 2003</amending-leg> (2003 No 119).</history-note>
